lead_paragraph: Ryder Cups are known for being one of the most highly charged occasions in sport and the 41st edition is poised for an electrifying launch at Hazeltine National on Friday in the opening foursomes.

headline.print_headline: Rose and Stenson to Lead Off for Holders Europe
